DumBot algorithm: 
-----------------
if (package here && i have room)
  xmit_pick_up_package(X);
  done();
elseif (me.empty?)
  me.target := closest package or unvisited homebase;
elseif (at destination for package X)
  xmit_drop_package(X);
  done();
else
  me.target := closest package, unvisted homebase, or delivery location;
end;

move towards me.target;


Required world-view support:
----------------------------
- Path-between algorithm
- Package tracking code
- Homebase visited flags
